::Slayer::

Slayer nods. "Yeah, we're gonna lead them to some hostile territory."

He looks back to see Atilla, Luzbel, and Shivah dive into the sea 
after the bot that Ignatius had scrapped. "Are they still following 
us?" he asks Ignatius, still heading toward the Cybertronian Fire.
